description: "Map of Asia with notes on the history of the region. Some place names are unusual: Sumatra = ‘Chersonese’, Philippines = ‘Iles Sabadibes’, Maluku Islands = ‘Iles Barusses’, Sunda Islands = ‘Iles Sindes’, Malay Peninsula = ‘Dorée’, Borneo = ‘Sinde I’."
title: "Carte de L'Asie selon les auteurs anciens enrichie de Remarques Historiques sur les changemens qui y sont arrivez"
